<p><strong><em>Fey Ancestry.</em></strong> The drow has advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic canâ€™t put the drow to sleep.</p>

<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> The drowâ€™s spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 11). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:</p>

